==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scribbler
<hw>Scrib"bler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who scribbles;
a petty author; a writer of no reputation; a literary hack.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>scribbler</qex>, pinched with hunger, writes to dine.</q>
<rj><qau>Granville.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scribbler</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Scribbler
<hw>Scrib"bler</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A scribbling machine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scribbling</ent>⟦br⟧
